<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08043h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08043h">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08043h"> 43(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ his shirt was pulled / aside from his chest / &amp; was told he was going / before his God</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Thomas McCarthy, a son of the last witness, told the story of how he was taken from his father&apos;s house, and at three different places placed on his knees and told to make an act of contrition. <mark>His shirt was pushed back from his chest and he was told he was going before his God</mark>. <small> <a name="II2jan24" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#II2jan24"><cite title="source">Irish Independent</cite></a> (2 January 1924) 5/4</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
